"> verser </operation> la sauce au <ingredient action="verser" quantite="400 gramme"> saumon </ingredient> / <ingredient action="verser" quantite="300 gramme"> crevettes </ingredient> / <ingredient action="verser" quantite=""> aneth </ingredient> dessus . <operation ingredients="parmesan"> saupoudrer </operation> abondament de <ingredient action="saupoudrer"> parmesan </ingredient> . bon app '
